ss by young boys and greet them with peace. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6247, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2168 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and\u00a0Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6183,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/10\/greet-peace-do-not-know\/","url_meta":{"origin":15427,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Islam: Greet strangers with peace","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 10, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr\u00a0reported: A man asked the Prophet, \u201cWhich Islam is best?\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThat you feed the hungry and you greet with peace those you know and those you do not know.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 28, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 39 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Featured&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Featured","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/featured\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15419,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/28\/gabriel-greet-peace\/","url_meta":{"origin":15427,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Jibre